_:node6af686a4d101098f419911fbe35d70 <http://schema.org/headline> "Bernie Madoff 'Hit the Inmate Lottery' with Butner Prison, Consultant Says" .
_:node6af686a4d101098f419911fbe35d70 <http://schema.org/genre> "News" .
_:node6af686a4d101098f419911fbe35d70 <http://schema.org/copyrightyear> "2009" .
